AB  - This paper presents monetary/fiscal multiplier results from the MPS Econometric Model which give irrepressible monetarist conclusions. Albert Ando's challenge to monetarist to develop their own model may now be reserved. Weak fiscal policy is supported by the MPS Model and reflects the dominant role of money in the short-run macro economic adjustment process.
